text.section:
A sponsor may satisfy the requirements of subsection (a)(1) of this section with materials developed under or in conjunction with:
The comprehensive plan for the jurisdiction reviewed and revised under § 1-416 or § 3-303 of the Land Use Article;
The local land preservation and recreation plan under § 5-905 of this title;
An approved local agricultural land preservation program under § 2-512 of the Agriculture Article, for the Maryland Agricultural Land Preservation Program;
An approved annual program submitted by the sponsor under Program Open Space;
An approved rural legacy area and grant agreement under the Rural Legacy Program under Subtitle 9A of this title;
The GreenPrint Program under Subtitle 15A of this title; or
Another acquisition plan prepared by, jointly funded, or accepted by the Department for the protection of local or State land preservation or recreational goals.
